1977;;Opening Night;;American;;John Cassavetes;;Gena Rowlands, Ben Gazzara, John Cassavetes;;drama;;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Opening_Night_(1977_film);;In the film, Broadway actress Myrtle Gordon rehearses for her latest play, about a woman unable to admit that she is aging. When she witnesses the death of an adoring young fan, she begins to confront the personal and professional turmoils she faces in her own life.